---
title: Sweet 'N' Spicy Meatloaves with Roasted Carrots and Potatoes
description: Think meatloaf is a fuddy-duddy? Think again: these mini pork meatloaves take a walk on the wild side with a spicy honey and ketchup glaze. It gives them just the right amount of heat and sweetness to make this meal extraordinary. And things only get more exciting when you consider the roasted carrots and buttery potatoes that take things into seriously satisfying territory.
